  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to examine the precision, bias and limits of agreement when
      monitoring the neuromuscular block with acceleromyography with and without preload and
      compare the method to the gold standard, mechanomyography.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
